OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783633273
OL,3,CDeveloper forced to demolish part of
OL,4,Chistoric hotel after court ruling
OL,6,FThe developer of the Raven Hotel has
OL,7,Fbeen ordered to demolish the non-
OL,8,Flisted part of the hotel and preserve
OL,9,Fthe historic part of the building
OL,10,Fafter the council won a legal claim
OL,11,Fagainst them.
OL,13,FIt's after the hotel in Droitwich Spa
OL,14,Fwas damaged in a fire in August 2025.
OL,16,FWest Mercia Police say that two girls
OL,17,Farrested on suspicion of arson for the
OL,18,Fincident have been released under
OL,19,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783633273
OL,3,CDeveloper forced to demolish part of
OL,4,Chistoric hotel after court ruling
OL,6,FITV News Central visited the hotel six
OL,7,Fmonths ago after a group of residents,
OL,8,Fknown as the Raven Heartbeat Group
OL,9,Flaunched their campaign to restore the
OL,10,Fcrumbling building.
OL,12,FNow Wychavon District Council, who
OL,13,Fhave been working with the group have
OL,14,Fwon their court case against the
OL,15,Fdeveloper, Live Urban Two limited
OL,16,Fwhich will mean they have to follow a
OL,17,Fclear timetable to demolish the
OL,18,Fdangerous parts of the building.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783633273
OL,3,CDeveloper forced to demolish part of
OL,4,Chistoric hotel after court ruling
OL,6,FThe order was granted at Kidderminster
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court on 26 June under
OL,8,Fsection 77 of the Building Act 1984
OL,9,Fand means that the council will have
OL,10,Fthe power to step in if the timetable
OL,11,Fis not met.
OL,13,FIt will also mean they have to make
OL,14,Fthe site safe again and restore the
OL,15,Fnon listed part of the hotel, which is
OL,16,F500 years old.
OL,18,FThe owner must seek pre-application
OL,19,Fadvice from Historic England and the
OL,20,Fcouncil about the demolition work by
OL,21,F10 July.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783633273
OL,3,CDeveloper forced to demolish part of
OL,4,Chistoric hotel after court ruling
OL,6,FRajinder Singh, a developer from Live
OL,7,FUrban Two limited told ITV News
OL,8,FCentral: "We are working with the
OL,9,Fcouncil to proceed with the
OL,10,Fdemolition. All our funds are in place
OL,11,Fand we are planning to submit
OL,12,Fsomething to the council on the 10th
OL,13,Fof July.
OL,15,F"A pre-application document is being
OL,16,Fprepared by our planning consultant
OL,17,Fand the construction company."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783633273
OL,3,CDeveloper forced to demolish part of
OL,4,Chistoric hotel after court ruling
OL,6,FThe council said requests for work
OL,7,Fwere sent in September 2025, January
OL,8,F2026 and again in May this year but
OL,9,Fthat no progress has been made.
OL,11,FPaul White who is an auctioneer and
OL,12,Fowns an antiques business at the back
OL,13,Fof the hotel, along with a number of
OL,14,Fother businesses said: "I am happy
OL,15,Fthat something is finally being done
OL,16,Fbecause something has to happen.
OL,18,F"The whole town feel that something
OL,19,Fneeds to be done because we are in a
OL,20,Flovely spa town and we have this eye
OL,21,Fsore in the town centre.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783633273
OL,3,CDeveloper forced to demolish part of
OL,4,Chistoric hotel after court ruling
OL,6,F"It's not the ideal situation because
OL,7,Fthe feeling is the council will have
OL,8,Fto step in and so the community will
OL,9,Fend up paying for it."
OL,11,FThe road around the hotel has been
OL,12,Fclosed since last August, meaning that
OL,13,FPaul has lost a lot of passing trade
OL,14,Fto his shop.
OL,16,FHe says his business has suffered as a
OL,17,Fresult, "We lost 30% of our turnover
OL,18,Fwhich equates to thousands of pounds
OL,19,Fbecause of the situation with the
OL,20,FRaven Hotel and we would like to see
OL,21,Fthings go back to normal.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783633273
OL,3,CDeveloper forced to demolish part of
OL,4,Chistoric hotel after court ruling
OL,6,F"I would of liked to see the developer
OL,7,Fdemolish the building."
OL,9,FDaniel Birch, a councillor for
OL,10,FWychavon District Council has also
OL,11,Fbeen actively involved with the
OL,12,Fcampaign group.
OL,14,FHe said: "It's a step in the right
OL,15,Fdirection but I don't have a great
OL,16,Fdegree of confidence that the
OL,17,Fdeveloper will take any action because
OL,18,Fthey haven't made any progress so far.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783633273
OL,3,CDeveloper forced to demolish part of
OL,4,Chistoric hotel after court ruling
OL,6,F"By the end of the year the non-listed
OL,7,Fpart part of the site will be
OL,8,Fdestroyed. We've had regular meetings
OL,9,Fto discuss the best way forward and
OL,10,Fit's not been an easy process.
OL,12,F"We have repeatedly asked the
OL,13,Fdeveloper to carry out the work and
OL,14,Fthey haven't listened. This has been
OL,15,Fthe result of a lot of work by the
OL,16,Fcouncil's legal team to get everything
OL,17,Ftogether and our hope is that any
OL,18,Fcosts incurred can be recovered.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783633273
OL,3,CDeveloper forced to demolish part of
OL,4,Chistoric hotel after court ruling
OL,6,F"The council has no obligation to
OL,7,Fpursue legal action but the community
OL,8,Fhas been a driving factor in making
OL,9,Fthis happen."
OL,11,FCllr Richard Morris, Leader of
OL,12,FWychavon, said: "The people of
OL,13,FDroitwich Spa deserve better than
OL,14,Fconstant excuses and false assurances.
OL,15,FI lost patience with the owner a long
OL,16,Ftime ago and have kept pushing for
OL,17,Fthis action, which draws a clear line
OL,18,Fin the sand.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/10
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1783633273
OL,3,CDeveloper forced to demolish part of
OL,4,Chistoric hotel after court ruling
OL,6,F"The owner now has a set timetable to
OL,7,Ffollow and we fully expect those
OL,8,Fdeadlines to be met. If not, we will
OL,9,Fnot hesitate to step in and do what is
OL,10,Fnecessary to protect this important
OL,11,Fhistoric building, which means so much
OL,12,Fto the town, and to finally start
OL,13,Fmoving forward towards the wider goal
OL,14,Fof redevelopment.
OL,16,F"We will be instructing officers to
OL,17,Fkeep the pressure on and engage with
OL,18,FHistoric England to get a clear
OL,19,Fpicture of progress made."
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU{D@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/10
